Class TagValuesSerializationUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.data.TagValuesSerializationUtil

  • public class TagValuesSerializationUtil
extends Object
    Utilities for serialization. Each ITagValue is serialized as "FIX bytes", i.e. tag + = + value + SOH.
